    {
      "text": "Dirt Trax FX is a racing video game developed by Sculptured Software and released by Acclaim Entertainment for the Super Nintendo Entertainment System in 1995. The 3D graphics of the game were made possible by the Super FX powered GSU-1, which was built into the cartridge.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Dirt Trax FX est un jeu vidéo de course développé par Sculptured Software et édité par Acclaim Entertainment, sorti en 1995 sur Super Nintendo. Il utilise la puce Super FX.",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikipedia_fr"
    },
    {
      "text": "Dirt Trax FX è un simulatore di guida del 1995 sviluppato da Sculptured Software per Super Nintendo Entertainment System.\nLa cartuccia del videogioco contiene il coprocessore matematico Super FX.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "Dirt Trax FXは、Sculptured Softwareが開発し、Acclaim Entertainmentから1995年にスーパーファミコン向けに発売されたレースビデオゲームです。このゲームの3Dグラフィックスは、カートリッジに内蔵されていたSuper FX搭載のGSU-1によって実現されました。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
